ygData.messageBody:
We are the Holy Crusaders

A group of adventurers that have banded together
to explore the land that is called Norrath

Our goal is a simple one have fun.

Our guild is predominantly made up of
paladins,clerics, and monks, but other races will
be admitted if they prove worthy.

Loyalty above all else is the deciding factor.

Come on in.
